of Love for the OutdoorsEntries were judged by a jury of leading film directors, producers, ad agency creatives and heads of production companies from around the world.  Winners will be announced at the eighth annual One Screen Short Film Festival ceremony on February 25, 2020 at the SVA Theater in New York.  Ticket information is available here.